OL,5, Energy firms have been failing         
OL,6, vulnerable customers, the sector's     
OL,7, watchdog has said, as people face a    
OL,8, cold and costly winter.                
OL,10,FOfgem told all 17 firms in its review  
OL,11,Fto improve, with Good Energy, Outfox,  
OL,12,FSo Energy, Tru Energy and Utilita found
OL,13,Fto have severe weaknesses.             
OL,15,FFailings included setting debt         
OL,16,Frepayments so high that customers could
OL,17,Fnot top-up their pre-payment meters.   
OL,19,FBut some of the suppliers hit back,    
OL,20,Fcalling the review "incomplete".       
